      "author": "arias007",
      "description": "Further improve Pdftion live ink rendering and zoom consistency.\\n\\n- Draw new ink segments incrementally during pointer movement instead of clearing and replaying the full page/stroke each frame.\\n- Scale displayed stroke width from the stroke's original page width to the current page width so zoom in/out keeps annotation proportions.\\n- Avoid layout-heavy overlay resize during active stroke redraws.\\n- Lower live stroke canvas DPR cap on high-density mobile screens to reduce input lag.",
      "downloadCount": 3,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "0.3.75",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-07-15T04:32:03Z",
      "tag": "0.3.75"
