      ],
      "author": "arias007",
      "description": "Fix Pdftion ink reliability and interaction performance.\\n\\n- Save editable ink state quickly after each stroke to reduce lost doodles.\\n- Coalesce overlay redraws and limit large-PDF redraw work to nearby pages.\\n- Observe PDF page/canvas resize so annotations track zoom changes.\\n- Densify stroke sampling to reduce lag-induced straight lines.\\n- Copy selected PDF text directly to the clipboard.\\n- Prevent empty/in-edit text annotations from being dragged before editing is committed.",
      "downloadCount": 2,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "0.3.74",
